            Press the Volume Up button to increase the volume, and press the Volume Down button to decrease the volume. 
            Long-press the Volume Up button for 3 seconds to switch between 3 scene modes - Normal mode, Noise cancelling mode, Outdoor mode.
          </p>
        </div>
       
